ue lenses and quick bug fixes were a regular thing. Here&#8217;s 2015 in a nutshell &#8211; SlideDeck 3.0 Released SlideDeck 3.1 Released SlideDeck Scheduler Addon Released Prime...\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Neha\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5164:\"<p>We&#8217;ve had a fabulous year, with some out-of-the-box releases and continuous updates. SlideDeck3 was launched in a brand new &#8211; faster, seo-friendly avatar. New addons, unique lenses and quick bug fixes were a regular thing. Here&#8217;s 2015 in a nutshell &#8211;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-3-0-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck 3.0 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-1-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck 3.1 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/scheduler-addon-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck Scheduler Addon Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/prime-lens-up-for-grabs/\" target=\"_blank\">Prime Lens Up For Grabs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/update-prime-lens-now-supports-all-14-dynamic-sources/\" target=\"_blank\">Update – Prime Lens Now Supports All 14 Dynamic Sources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/importexport-slider-addon-released/\" target=\"_blank\">Import / Export Slider Addon Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/create-sliders-on-any-website-using-the-slidedeck-app/\" target=\"_blank\">Create sliders on any website using the SlideDeck App</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/update-pinterest-pin-it-button-now-on-your-slidedecks/\" target=\"_blank\">Update – Pinterest Pin It Button Now on Your Slidedecks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-2-4-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck 3.2.4 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/parfocal-lens-get-your-slider-images-moving-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Parfocal Lens – Get your slider images moving</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-2-6-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck 3.2.6 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/there-is-intelligent-life-in-this-slider/\" target=\"_blank\">Launching new Lead Generation Addon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-now-integrates-with-woocommerce-products/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck 3 now integrates with WooCommerce Products</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck3-3-3-2-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck 3.3.2 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-3-will-try-to-fix-you/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck Version 3.3.3 will try to fix you</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-4-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck Version 3.3.4 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-5-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck Version 3.3.5 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/roses-in-december-share-warmth-with-sliders-that-go-viral/\" target=\"_blank\">Roses in December – Share warmth with sliders that go viral</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/a-brand-new-lens-with-parallax-effect/\" target=\"_blank\">A brand new lens with Parallax effect</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-4-1-released/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDe