:\"SlideDeck 3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Tips & Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"http://www.slidedeck.com/?p=17297\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:284:\"The Parallax Lens lets you create Parallax effect  sliders . Here&#8217;s a quick guide on how to use the Parallax Lens : The Parallax lens has 2 effects: Scroll movement &#8211; A caption image on a base image. Mouse movement &#8211; 3 layer images and 1 caption image which move...\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Neha\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4528:\"<p>The <strong><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/a-brand-new-lens-with-parallax-effect/\" target=\"_blank\">Parallax Lens</a></strong> lets you create Parallax effect  sliders . Here&#8217;s a quick guide on how to use the Parallax Lens :</p>\n<p>The Parallax lens has 2 effects:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Scroll movement</strong> &#8211; A caption image on a base image.</li>\n<li><strong>Mouse movement</strong> &#8211; 3 layer images and 1 caption image which move as the mouse hovers on the base image. The position of these images has to be adjusted at the backend.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>STEP ONE-</strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>Manage-&gt;Custom Content-&gt;Image Slide</em></strong></p>\n<p>Select custom image slide in custom content source.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-17299 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/manage-custom-580x105.png\" alt=\"manage-&gt;custom\" width=\"580\" height=\"105\" /></p>\n<p><strong>STEP TWO &#8211;</strong></p>\n<p><em><strong>Options-&gt;Lenses-&gt;Parallax Lens</strong></em></p>\n<p>Select the Parallax Lens in lenses</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-17300 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/selectparallax-580x257.png\" alt=\"selectparallax\" width=\"580\" height=\"257\" /></p>\n<p><strong>STEP THREE &#8211;</strong></p>\n<p>Hover on the slide and select &#8216;Click to edit&#8217;</p>\n<p>For Scroll movement Parallax effect, upload the base image and the caption image and specify the movement depth</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-17301 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scrolltute-580x383.png\" alt=\"scrolltute\" width=\"580\" height=\"383\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-17276 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-parallax.png\" alt=\"scroll parallax\" width=\"575\" height=\"275\" /></p>\n<p><strong>STEP FOUR &#8211;</strong></p>\n<p>For Mouse movement Parallax effect, upload the base image, the 3 layer images and the caption image</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-17302 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mousetute-580x520.png\" alt=\"mousetute\" width=\"580\" height=\"520\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-large wp-image-17275 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mouse-movement-parallax-580x280.png\" alt=\"Mouse Movement Parallax\" width=\"580\" height=\"280\" /></p>\n<p>Adjust the position of layer images and the caption. You can also add opacity to the layer images. Select &#8216;Save&#8217;</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it. You have a Parallax effect slider ready.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://demo.slidedeck.com/custom-slidedeck-parallax-lens/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-17303 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/unnamed.png\" alt=\"View Examples\" width=\"182\" height=\"46\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://demo.slidedeck.com/wp-login.php\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-17277 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Try-the-free-demoButton.png\" alt=\"Try the free demo\" width=\"182\" height=\"46\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<br/><br/><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog\"><img src=\"//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg\" alt=\"Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck\" style=\"display:block;border:none;\"/></a><div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=dXDhg7lySlM:Trg6vam90dA:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\">